skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: leslie voice
des:
This skill provides you with basic information about St. Philomena's College Mysore and Fr. Leslie Moras, a former principal of the college.

You can say "Alexa ask leslie voice " followed by one of the following,
"tell me about the college",
"tell me about the history of the college",
"where is the college located",
"who inaugurated the college",
"tell me about the courses available",
"tell me about the facilities available",
"tell me about fr. leslie"
"Where was he born",
"where is he now",
"where did he study",
"begin playback",
"launch gallery"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
